{
  "3092110": {
    "name": "地牢与王国",
    "steam_appid": 3092110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/31a1c6d6dae3d896138cb2231583ca96.poster.avif?t=1766365601\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/31a1c6d6dae3d896138cb2231583ca96.webm?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/31a1c6d6dae3d896138cb2231583ca96.mp4?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《地牢与王国》融合了中世纪奇幻策略游戏与角色扮演游戏的重要元素。你将率领一伙难民逃离无法生活的家乡，远渡重洋到达新的世界，开始全新生活。你可以亲力亲为，参与一切的建设，也可以构画图纸，命令忠诚的拓殖者大兴土木。建设领地，满足大家的需求，采集资源，种植作物，猎杀野物，竭尽全力生存下去。<br><br>然后深入危险的地牢，面对盘踞其中的怪物。探索每一间牢房，考验自身的战斗能力，击败地牢的头目，最终收获奖励，解锁新的资源，推进技术发展。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合抱之木，生于毫末</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/453377792ab0cf187b8f4cf9d12fefde.poster.avif?t=1766365601\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/453377792ab0cf187b8f4cf9d12fefde.webm?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/453377792ab0cf187b8f4cf9d12fefde.mp4?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>外出觅食，种植作物，确保村民的基本生活。制作工具，采收资源，搭建遮风挡雨的简易建筑和早期建筑，推进领地的经济发展。你要直面逼真的昼夜循环，渡过春夏秋冬，积累宝贵的知识，学习宝贵的技能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设你的村庄</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/7b09cfca8d41341d6237a7d617511690.poster.avif?t=1766365601\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/7b09cfca8d41341d6237a7d617511690.webm?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/7b09cfca8d41341d6237a7d617511690.mp4?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>模块化建筑系统供你升级和搭建与众不同的建筑。500多个建筑元素各不相同，随意搭配，抢先体验期间还会有更多建筑元素加进游戏。可以从零开始设计建筑，也可以绘制图纸，而后可以编辑、改进，甚至可以分享到Steam的创意工坊。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >娴熟改造地形</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/06652e1cff85e6b8f508791b76ded252.poster.avif?t=1766365601\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/06652e1cff85e6b8f508791b76ded252.webm?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/06652e1cff85e6b8f508791b76ded252.mp4?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>雕凿地形，以便你的乡亲在这里生活。压平大片土地用于耕种，抬高降低陆台方便土木建设，填充河谷，挖掘护城河和沟壕。给大地刷上郁郁葱葱的草木，也可以抹去花草树木，以便铺砌道路，搭建楼房，供人们生活。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为了王国而战</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/dabe03c423616aa18f934cd48f476a76.poster.avif?t=1766365601\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/dabe03c423616aa18f934cd48f476a76.webm?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/dabe03c423616aa18f934cd48f476a76.mp4?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>消灭围墙之外的祸患。开展冒险角色扮演游戏风格的第三人称战斗，猎杀野兽，保证村民不受饥饿困扰，驱逐土匪，保护官道畅通。保卫你的人民，守护你的土地，培养自己在疆域之外的威势。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深入地牢</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/9a9850f6433a0dcf4a95b785a943f5a6.poster.avif?t=1766365601\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/9a9850f6433a0dcf4a95b785a943f5a6.webm?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092110/extras/9a9850f6433a0dcf4a95b785a943f5a6.mp4?t=1766365601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索古老的遗迹和神庙，面对盘踞其中的怪物。探索每一间牢房，考验自身的战斗能力，击败地牢的头目，最终收获奖励，推进王国技术的发展。",
